extendedInfo.description: Android's first true real-time, online, multiplayer game. Check out this MMORPG top down shooter!Features:-- True real-time gameplay-- Up to 24 players in a single game-- Multiple character types-- Customizable character stats-- Multiple maps and game modes-- Player forum at www.chickenbrickstudios.com/forum/-- Music and sound effects-- Much moreKeywords: real time, player vs player, pvp, shooter, top down, multiplayer, multi player, online, networked, military, mmorpg, mmo, rpg, action, friends, chat, social, level up, medic, scout, marine, brute, potions, abilities, skills, music, sound, stats, skill tree

reviews.title: Could be better.
reviews.comment: The biggest problem I have is that almost nobody plays it (the most I\'ve ever seen online at once was 10) and everybody always plays the \"The Hospital\" map over and over again. It\'s also pretty laggy, even over wifi. I know you can\'t necessarily change the amount of people who play or the maps that those who do play choose, but still...
reviews.author: Rhonda Davenport

reviews.title: Cmon already!
reviews.comment: This game is in dire need of something new. I\'ve had this installed on 3 phones over the last 5 years and all we\'ve been given is one new (lousy) class. I love this game, but FFS, please give us a new map or something! I\'d be more than happy to donate some cash to ignite some renewed interest on the devs part if it would bring us some new content. Please Chicken Brick, your devoted fans are bored and restless!
reviews.author: A Google User
